data.description: Welcome to this charming and cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a warm and inviting atmosphere. Located right across from Campbell's Flowers on the southside, this residence offers the perfect combination of functionality and style. Step inside, and you'll find yourself in the heart of the home – an open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area. The layout creates a sense of spaciousness, allowing for effortless flow and interaction between the different areas. The master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom for added convenience. Outside, the backyard provides a patio area – perfect for enjoying the fresh air and sunshine. The low-maintenance landscaping allows for easy upkeep, leaving more time to savor the joys of home. This residence not only offers a comfortable and stylish living space but also provides the convenience of proximity to local amenities, schools, and parks. With its open-concept design and thoughtful details, this 3-bed, 2-bath home invites you to create lasting memories in a place that truly feels like home.
